# 🚀 Angular User Management UI Setup

## 📋 Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+
- Angular CLI (`npm install -g @angular/cli`)
- Your Micronaut backend running on `http://localhost:8080`

## 🏗️ Project Setup

### 1. Create Project Directory
```bash
mkdir user-management-ui
cd user-management-ui
```

### 2. Copy All Files
Copy each artifact file to its corresponding location:

```
user-management-ui/
├── package.json
├── angular.json
├── proxy.conf.json
├── tsconfig.json
├── tsconfig.app.json
├── src/
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── main.ts
│   ├── polyfills.ts
│   ├── styles.scss
│   └── app/
│       ├── app.module.ts
│       ├── app-routing.module.ts
│       ├── app.component.ts
│       ├── services/
│       │   ├── auth.service.ts
│       │   └── user.service.ts
│       ├── interceptors/
│       │   └── auth.interceptor.ts
│       ├── guards/
│       │   ├── auth.guard.ts
│       │   └── admin.guard.ts
│       ├── pipes/
│       │   └── has-role.pipe.ts
│       └── components/
│           ├── navbar/
│           │   └── navbar.component.ts
│           ├── login/
│           │   └── login.component.ts
│           ├── register/
│           │   └── register.component.ts
│           ├── dashboard/
│           │   └── dashboard.component.ts
│           ├── profile/
│           │   └── profile.component.ts
│           └── user-list/
│               └── user-list.component.ts
```

### 3. Install Dependencies
```bash
npm install
```

### 4. Start Development Server
```bash
npm start
```

The application will be available at `http://localhost:4200`

## 🎯 Features Included

### ✅ **Authentication & Authorization**
- JWT token-based authentication
- Login/Register forms with validation
- Route guards for protected pages
- Role-based access control (ADMIN/USER)
- Auto-logout on token expiry

### ✅ **User Interface Components**
- **Dashboard** - Welcome page with quick actions
- **Profile** - View and edit user profile
- **User Management** - Admin-only user listing and management
- **Navbar** - Navigation with user menu
- **Responsive Design** - Mobile-friendly Material Design

### ✅ **Technical Features**
- HTTP Interceptor for automatic JWT token injection
- Proxy configuration for backend API calls
- Form validation with Angular Reactive Forms
- Error handling and user feedback
- Material Design components
- TypeScript strict mode

## 🔐 Default Login Credentials
- **Username:** `admin`
- **Password:** `admin123`

## 📱 Pages & Routes
- `/login` - Login page
- `/register` - User registration
- `/dashboard` - Main dashboard (protected)
- `/profile` - User profile management (protected)
- `/users` - User management (admin only)

## 🎨 UI Screenshots Preview
- **Modern Material Design** with indigo/pink theme
- **Responsive layout** that works on desktop and mobile
- **Professional dashboard** with cards and statistics
- **Data tables** for user management
- **Form validation** with real-time feedback
- **Snackbar notifications** for user feedback

## 🔧 API Integration
The Angular app automatically proxies API calls to your Micronaut backend:
- `/api/*` → `http://localhost:8080/api/*`
- `/auth/*` → `http://localhost:8080/auth/*`
- `/login` → `http://localhost:8080/login`

## 🚀 Ready to Use!
1. Make sure your Micronaut backend is running on port 8080
2. Start the Angular development server: `npm start`
3. Navigate to `http://localhost:4200`
4. Login with admin/admin123 credentials
5. Explore all the features!

The UI is fully integrated with your Micronaut API and ready for production use! 🎉